-------> WELCOME (5min)

Welcome to our inaugural fellowship service at Be The Church 624

My name is Nick and I have the honour of leading this ministry and this weekly fellowship service held every Thursday starting at 8pm ET

This ministry was created because my wife and I had an unmet desire to study scripture and be in community with fellow Christians around the world who align in the quest to live biblically

We believe striving to understand the word of God and live righteously in a world of sin is best achieved in fellowship with other believers

From that belief, we created BTC624 as a way to build a global community that offers strength in numbers and a means of perseverance in maintaining faith to the end 

We want this fellowship service to be a high signal, valuable offering which means they will be highly structured and the structure will evolve over time based on feeback from our fellows and listeners

Todays session will go like this:
- 5 minute welcome
- 2 minute opening prayer
- 20 minutes of scripture
- 10 minute discussion on behaviour, today we're talking about the specific behaviour of reading the bible
- 10 minute discussion on stewardship, today we're talking about sinful currency
- 2min closing prayer
- 10 min stories/discussion (optional)

In future we will have a 30 minute cyber social after the service and worship music leading up to our 8pm start



-------> OPENING PRAYER (2min)

Heavenly Father, hallowed is your name

May your kingdom come and your will be done on earth as it is in heaven

We ask father that you meet all of our daily needs, that you forgive our sins and that you bless us with a willingness to forgive those who have sinned against us

We pray that you bless our fellowship gathering today, that you protect us from evil and that you lead us away from fleshly temptations

In Jesus name

Amen



